<item>
            <title>[LU-6836] sanity-quota test_4a: Passed grace time 12, 1436542665, 1436542679</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6836</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Bob Glossman &amp;lt;bob.glossman@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/5028e598-274b-11e5-9632-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/5028e598-274b-11e5-9632-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_4a failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Passed grace time 12, 1436542665, 1436542679
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This seems very related to &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4306&quot; title=&quot;Test failure sanity-quota test_4a: failed create before timer expired&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4306&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4306&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.  The same test is failing, but the error message is new and in fresh lines from recent landing in master for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4306&quot; title=&quot;Test failure sanity-quota test_4a: failed create before timer expired&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4306&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4306&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanity-quota 4a&lt;/p&gt;</description>
